summary: This is a brief email forwarding FBI 302 interview reports (likely related to the Epstein investigation) and requesting they be saved to designated Epstein folders. It indicates internal handling of investigative documents.

events.title: Email Forwarding FBI 302s
events.description: An email is sent forwarding FBI 302 interview reports with a request to save them to Epstein case folders.

keyFacts: FBI 302 interview reports were being circulated internally on December 10, 2019.
The email indicates a request to organize these documents into specific 'Epstein folders'.
The correspondence shows ongoing handling of investigative materials related to the Epstein case.
